title: President receives delegation of U.S. doctors (The President of the Republic of Armenia)
text: ( Source : The President of the Republic of Armenia ) President Serzh Sargsyan received today the delegation of highly-experienced U.S. doctors who have visited Armenia from 5 to 15 October on the initiative of Berj Apkarian , RA Honorary
